========ENGLISH=======
See doc/manual.pdf (in Chinese) for information about this program.

* HOW TO USE:

If you get the source tree from the git repo, you need xelatex
(usually from texlive) to compile doc/manual.pdf.  Then, you need GNU
Autotools and run:

   ./autogen.sh

before you follow the instructions in INSTALL.

If you get a tarball (such as a file ended with .tar.gz), you need to
unpack it then follow the instructions in INSTALL.  Fortunately,
doc/manual.pdf is already there for your reference.

For a short version of INSTALL, running

    ./configure
    make
    make install

when you're in the source directory will install the program to your
computer.  Note that you need to have proper previlage to run the last
command.  In many cases, this means running:

    sudo make install

instead of just "make install".

========CHINESE=======
请参阅 doc/manual.pdf (中文) 来了解此程序。

* 如何使用：

如果你从GIT仓库获取此程序的源代码，你需要 xelatex (通常来自 texlive 程
序包) 来生成 doc/manual.pdf。接着你需要 GNU Autotools，并在源码目录下运
行：

    ./autogen.sh

然后再继续参阅 INSTALL 文件。

如果你获取的是一个扩展名类似 .tar.gz 的压缩包，你需要解压它，再继续参阅
INSTALL 文件。doc/manual.pdf此时已经存在于压缩包中，供你参阅。

INSTALL 文件中的内容简单来说，就是在源代码文件夹下运行：

    ./configure
    make
    make install

这样，程序就安装在电脑中了。请注意，你需要有合适的权限来运行最后一条命
令。在很多情况下，这意味着要运行

    sudo make install

而不是"make install"。